---
import ClientReportLayout from '../../../layouts/ClientReportLayout.astro';
---

<ClientReportLayout title="Research Process" clientName="1st Home Maintenance">
<nav class="top-nav">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/clients/zolley/" class="nav-brand">Brothers Automate</a>
    <a href="/clients/zolley/">&larr; Back to Overview</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-badge">Our Research Process</div>
    <h1>How We Built This Analysis</h1>
    <p>AI-powered research across 35+ data sources, synthesized into clear findings and actionable recommendations.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="steps-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <div class="section-label">4-Step Process</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">From Data Collection to Actionable Insights</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h3>SEO & Technical Audit</h3>
        <p>We analyzed your website's technical health, keyword rankings, competitor landscape, and search visibility across all major search engines.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h3>Company Intelligence</h3>
        <p>We researched your business profile, online reputation, brand mentions, and competitive positioning in the Boca Raton handyman market.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h3>Local Maps & Search</h3>
        <p>We checked your Google Maps presence, local pack rankings, competitor reviews, and local search visibility across all relevant queries.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <h3>Social & Reviews</h3>
        <p>We audited your presence across all major social platforms, review sites, business directories, and industry-specific listing sites.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="data-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <div class="section-label">Data Points Analyzed</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">What We Looked At</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="data-grid">
      <div class="data-card">
        <h3>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3182ce" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
          Search & SEO
        </h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Keyword rankings and search positions</li>
          <li>Search volume and keyword difficulty</li>
          <li>Competitor keyword overlap analysis</li>
          <li>Site performance and page speed scores</li>
          <li>Technical SEO health (meta tags, headers, schema)</li>
          <li>Website technology stack detection</li>
          <li>Content depth and page-level analysis</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="data-card">
        <h3>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3182ce" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          Local Presence
        </h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Google Business Profile status</li>
          <li>Google Maps ranking positions</li>
          <li>Local pack competitor analysis</li>
          <li>Review counts and ratings across platforms</li>
          <li>Citation and directory listings</li>
          <li>Local search trends and demand</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="data-card">
        <h3>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3182ce" stroke-width="2"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
          Social & Reputation
        </h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Facebook, Instagram, Yelp, BBB presence</li>
          <li>Active advertising and paid media</li>
          <li>Online brand mentions and sentiment</li>
          <li>Competitor social activity and engagement</li>
          <li>Review platform coverage audit</li>
          <li>Contact and communication channels</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="timeline-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Analysis Timeline</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">How This Report Came Together</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Our AI-powered research system ran 4 parallel analysis streams simultaneously.</p>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-time">Step 1 (0:00)</div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h4>Research Initiated</h4>
        <p>All four analysis agents began simultaneously, each focused on a different dimension of your online presence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-time">Step 2 (0:05)</div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h4>Data Collection Complete</h4>
        <p>SEO data, company intelligence, local Maps rankings, and social/review data all collected and verified.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-time">Step 3 (0:10)</div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h4>Cross-Reference & Analysis</h4>
        <p>Findings from all four streams were cross-referenced to identify patterns, confirm gaps, and prioritize opportunities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-time">Step 4 (0:15)</div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h4>Reports Generated</h4>
        <p>Final reports synthesized with actionable recommendations, competitive benchmarks, and a prioritized roadmap.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Questions About Our Findings?</h2>
    <p>We're happy to walk you through the data and answer any questions you have about the analysis.</p>
    <a href="https://cal.com/james-pinder-simpleflo/free-quiz-audit-automation-brothers" class="btn-cta">
      Book a Free Strategy Call
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">Prepared by Brothers Automate &middot; April 2026</div>
</footer>
</ClientReportLayout>

<style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; background: #fdfcfa; color: #1a365d; line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

    .top-nav { padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e6e1; background: #ffffff; }
    .top-nav .container { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .top-nav a { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .top-nav a:hover { color: #1a365d; }
    .nav-brand { font-weight: 700; color: #1a365d !important; }

    .hero {
      padding: 100px 0 60px;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a5f 0%, #3182ce 50%, #1e40af 100%);
      color: white;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      border-radius: 9999px; padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4.5vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #ed8936; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .section-title { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .section-subtitle { color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

    /* Steps */
    .steps-section { padding: 80px 0; }
    .steps-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .steps-grid::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 40px;
      left: 12.5%;
      width: 75%;
      height: 2px;
      background: #e8e6e1;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .step-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e8e6e1;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .step-number {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: #1a365d;
      color: white; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .step-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .step-card p { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.875rem; }

    /* Data Points */
    .data-section {
      padding: 60px 0;
      background: #f8f7f4;
    }
    .data-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .data-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e8e6e1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .data-card h3 {
      font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .data-card ul {
      list-style: none; padding: 0;
    }
    .data-card li {
      padding: 0.3rem 0;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #64748b;
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .data-card li::before {
      content: '';
      width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: #3182ce;
      position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.65rem;
    }

    /* Timeline */
    .timeline-section { padding: 60px 0; }
    .timeline-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0eeea;
    }
    .timeline-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .timeline-time {
      min-width: 120px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #3182ce;
    }
    .timeline-content h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .timeline-content p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #64748b; }

    .cta-section { background: #1a365d; padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; color: white; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .cta-section p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .btn-cta {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: #ed8936; color: white; padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none; transition: all 200ms ease;
    }
    .btn-cta:hover { background: #dd6b20; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .footer { padding: 2rem 0; text-align: center; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px solid #e8e6e1; }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .steps-grid::before { display: none; }
      .data-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .timeline-item { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
    var elements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up');
    if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
      var observer = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
        entries.forEach(function (entry) {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add('visible');
            observer.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        });
      }, { threshold: 0.15 });
      elements.forEach(function (el) { observer.observe(el); });
    } else {
      elements.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('visible'); });
    }
  });
</script>
